edu.cuny.event
Class EventEngine

java.lang.Object
  edu.cuny.event.EventEngine

public class EventEngine
extends java.lang.Object

Provides a mechnism for synchronized event dispatching of Events.

The class is synchronized, so be careful in multithreading scenario to avoid deadlock.
